oActionText":18,"callToActionLink":18,"colorStyle":187,"showAsides":188,"imageUrl":189,"__component":225},27,"Teams","Innoveer je samenwerking","De meeste mensen zijn al bekend met het online vergaderen binnen Teams. Maar er zijn nog veel meer mogelijkheden om de samenwerking binnen je organisatie te verbeteren met een goede Microsoft Teams-implementatie. Onze consultants kunnen de manier van werken met Teams binnen jouw organisatie verbeteren met behulp van verschillende Teams apps zoals Planner, OneNote, Loop en meer. Daarnaast kunnen zij best practices opstellen en helpen bij het implementeren van de nieuwste Teams-innovaties. Met hun kennis kunnen onze consultants op directieniveau meedenken en adviseren over de juiste Teams implementatie. ","Sugar Glaze",false,{"id":190,"name":191,"alternativeText":18,"caption":18,"width":19,"height":192,"formats":193,"hash":220,"ext":23,"mime":197,"size":221,"url":222,"previewUrl":18,"provider":54,"provider_metadata":18,"createdAt":223,"updatedAt":223,"documentId":224,"publishedAt":57,"focalPoint":18},782,"Teams.jpg",850,{"large":194,"small":201,"medium":207,"thumbnail":213},{"ext":23,"url":195,"hash":196,"mime":197,"name":198,"path":18,"size":199,"width":29,"height":200},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/large_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","large_Teams_43eca91eed","image/jpeg","large_Teams.jpg",75.76,664,{"ext":23,"url":202,"hash":203,"mime":197,"name":204,"path":18,"size":205,"width":20,"height":206},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/small_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","small_Teams_43eca91eed","small_Teams.jpg",24.28,332,{"ext":23,"url":208,"hash":209,"mime":197,"name":210,"path":18,"size":211,"width":42,"height":212},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.strapiapp.com/medium_Teams_43eca91eed.jpg","medium_Teams_43eca91eed","medium_Teams.jpg",45.38,498,{"ext":23,"url":214,"hash":215,"mime":197,"name":216,"path":18,"size":217,"width":218,"height":219},"https://incredible-beef-2a6059b946.media.st